# Current Goals & Roadmap (June 2026)

## Active Work Streams (In Progress)

### Insight Hub (Conversational Insight) — SHIPPED both lines
- Standalone hubs live: Pro (`mind-measure-pro-insight-hub` → insight.mindmeasurepro.com) and University (`mind-measure-university-insight-hub` → insight.mindmeasure.co.uk). University hub is done and functional.
- Lets an institution pose natural-language questions that Jodie weaves into check-ins, then reads back anonymised themes, sentiment and cohort divergence. K-anonymity floor of five.
- Thin UI proxy: no business logic in the hubs; they SSO-handoff from admin and proxy to the `/api/companies/*` (Pro) / equivalent (Uni) Conversational Insight endpoints in the core repos.
- Gated per institution by `conversational_insight_enabled` boolean.
- Full docs: `mind-measure-docs/pages/insight-hub/` and section 10 of the Pro Employer Handbook (`handbook-pro.mdx`).

### Marketing Website Polish
- Corporate site (`mindmeasurepro.com`) and university site (`mindmeasure.co.uk`) both live
