## Roadmap — Active Planning

### Cohort Template Library (HIGH — sprint candidate)
Evolve cohort analysis from localStorage build-it-yourself tool into a shared library of reusable, live-data cohort views. Users build configurations once, publish to a browsable library, always populated with current data.
- Phase 1: Custom titles, migrate localStorage → `saved_cohort_templates` DB table
- Phase 2: Live data population via `UniversityDataService`
- Phase 3: Library UI — browse, search, load published templates
- Phase 4: Historical overlay (same cohort across time periods)
- Phase 5: Institutional starter packs

### Streak Rewards (HIGH — spec to be written)
Digital voucher rewards for consistent check-in habits. Partner retailer integration creates sponsorship revenue.

### Student Ambassador Platform (HIGH — spec to be written)
Social media assets library + ambassador signup/management system. Referral tracking, performance dashboards, bonus payouts.

### Auth Token Standardisation (MEDIUM — planning)
Align university and pro mobile apps on same token pattern (`cognitoApiClient`). Feeds into shared auth package.

### Score Reveal Interaction (MEDIUM — spec written)
UX theatre for post-check-in score display. Brief transition screen ("Preparing your results"), then animated gauge reveal with scoring band highlight and one-line interpretation. Keeps it to 1–2 seconds — intentional pause, not a delay.

### Load Testing (MEDIUM — not started)
Load test full check-in flow at 100+ concurrent users. Identify bottlenecks in Bedrock/Rekognition throttling and Aurora connections.

